Package: uvr
Title: R Interface to the 'uvr' Package Manager
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Francesco", "Grazzini", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "francesco@example.com")
Description: Provides R functions that wrap the 'uvr' command-line tool for
    fast, reproducible R package management. Functions include project
    initialization, package addition and removal, lockfile synchronization,
    and script execution within isolated environments. Requires the 'uvr'
    binary to be installed separately.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    jsonlite,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
